reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Nice starter set
reviews.reviewText: This set comes exactly as described. The makeup seems to be pretty nice too. The lipsticks are a nice formula, and good color. The amount you get would be great for introducing someone to makeup - plenty to play with and try! Or, if you want to expand your personal makeup choices, this is a great kit. Not necessarily good for travel though, as the kit is a little large.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars This is a holiday gift for every girl
reviews.reviewText: My daughter recently turned 9 years old, and my wife and I decided to buy her this beautiful set as a birthday present. My daughter was crazy with happiness, this is a great set for girls, it looks great, but the most important thing is not the appearance, but the quality, the child has no irritation on the face after using this cosmetics, there are no allergies, as often happens on children's skin after using cosmetics. This is a high-quality and beautiful product for girls.
